title: Introducing the new Fox V4 Helmet
description:
In creating the V4 helmet, Fox exceeded the needs of the world's most demanding sport, Motocross. If you're serious about motocross, this is your helmet. Watch as Fox riders Ryan Dungey, Ken Roczen, Chad Reed and Ricky Carmichael take the V4 for a ride. The V4 is the Pinnacle of Performance.

For more info about the V4 Helmet go to: http://www.foxhead.com/v4/
